{"type": "article", "id": 3287, "title": "Daniel Becker 45  Series 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-05T08:33:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004213I2Bor467QidManGc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以旧造新这个概念在设计界早已不新奇，柏林设计工作室 Daniel Becker 近日带来一组家具 45 Series Collection，包括一个凳子与一个橱柜，皆由使用过的平整的木质货板材料制作而成，设计师将这些木板拆卸、分割，并进行全新的组装，排列成不同的几何图案和形状。Daniel Becker 表示：“我们希望这组设计能能够打开人们关于回收利用概念的想像力，用最传统的木工工艺，创造出有趣的大众都能够负担得起的产品。”定价 155 欧元，<a href=\"http://contemporarycomponents.bigcartel.com/product/kimidori-45-stool-side-table-monochrome\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004211MOb1eHuPTdc5kNYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004211UC6pTM4cdtKrnzhq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004212qPkghjLGax2wNXA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004212Ko20OHqu7Mc4tZxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004212jgk6Ix2c0hMlbNdq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}